FBIS4-65144 "drweu092cc_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-092 Daily Report 11 May 1994 INTER-EUROPEAN AFFAIRS EU Issues `Urgent Appeal' To Halt Fighting in Yemen EU Issues `Urgent Appeal' To Halt Fighting in Yemen AU1105151194 Paris AFP in English 1458 GMT 11 May 94 AU1105151194 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Brussels, May 11 (AFP) -- The European Union [EU] issued an urgent appeal Wednesday [11 May] to warring parties in Yemen to put an early end to hostilities. A statement issued here voiced "deep concern" about the fighting between north and south. It said the fighting should stop in the spirit of an agreement on reconciliation and reform signed in February.
